## Components to Build
- FinanceDashboardShell
  - Layout container with left navigation, top bar, and content region
  - Persisted UI state (collapsed sidebar, active tab, user preferences)

- SnapshotTiles
  - Cards showing Balance, Monthly Spend, Forecast, and Savings Opportunities
  - Data-driven with currency formatting, growth indicators, and drill-through actions

- TransactionsOverview
  - Transaction Feed with: search, filter, categorized grouping, tag chips
  - Manual Categorization UI (drag/assign or select)
  - Create Categorization Rules modal
  - Exceptions marking (unmatched or review-needed)

- SubscriptionsPanel
  - List of user-owned and tracked subscriptions
  - Churn risk indicators, spend limit warnings
  - Connect Billing Processors UI (add/remove connectors, OAuth flows)

- AnomaliesPanel
  - Real-time/near-real-time anomaly alerts with severity
  - Agent-provided rationale, suggested remediation, and acknowledgement actions

- ForecastingPanel
  - Time-series charts with selectable horizons and scenarios
  - ROI/impact indicators and scenario comparison

- MonthlyClosePanel
  - Checklists, reconciliations, auto-generated tasks
  - Approval queue integration and audit trails

- AgentRecommendationsPanel
  - Contextual recommendations with confidence scores
  - Actionable steps, expected ROI, and reversible actions

- FinanceAutomationBridge
  - Orchestrates ingestion, categorization, anomaly detection, forecasting, and monthly close workflows
  - Exposes status and traces for each workflow run

